		   <tr><td class="headerrow" colspan="2" class="mform" valign="top" id="forumSubject">Necromancer<br clear="all" /><script type="text/javascript">document.title = document.title + ": Thread: Necromancer";</script>
		   <span class="sm">Posted @ Tue, Jul 15th 6:36 PM2003 </span><span id="notbold">| <span class="sm">IP: Logged</span> | <a href="/db/classes.html?class=14&mid=105830801647400&post=1"><a class="sm" href="/db/classes.html?class=14&mid=105830801647400&post=1&replyto=105830801647400"><img src="/shared/reply_to_thread_ico.gif" border="0" alt="Reply..." height="11" width="17" /> Reply to this</a></a>    <a name=105830801647400></a></small></td></tr>
		   <tr><td valign="top" id="fs8" class="mform" ><span id="notbold">By:</span> <a href="/db/poster.html?user=244869"><span id=>extasye</span></a><b><span id=></span></b><br />2 posts
		   <br /><nobr><span id="notbold">Score</span>: Decent [3.00]</nobr><br /><br /><a href="/cgi-bin/pm.pl?action=addtolist&addname=extasye&type=Address" id="fs8"><img src="/shared/plus.gif" border="0" align="middle" height="9" width="9" alt="Add to address book"> Add to address book</a><br /><img src="/shared/transp.gif" width="135" border="0" height="1"></td><td valign="top" class="mform" width="100%"><p><br>Well, just a few things to say ... first of all I am a level 65 Arch Lich so I have some exp playing a necromancer, but still it is only my opinions and we all have them ...<br><br>Picking your starting race; My personal favorites though are Iksar and Dark Elf (I am Dark Elf btw they didn't even have Iksar when I made my necro) Well this truly isn't important because in the end game the gear you get makes everyone basically equal or just as good as the next necromancer. Also Iksar regen and better starting stats doesn't really matter in end game either because you get such good life taps and life drain Dots that regen isnt even an issue ... <br>If you want a fast xp gain with high int with ultra vision then pick dark elf ... If you want easier leveling but much longer time leveling with regen, forage and 100 starting swim and A LOT better starting stats then pick Iksar ... I know they only start with 110int but the other stats make up for it and int gear is super easy to get anyway ... As far as the other races, well I don't like them myself so I won't talk about them since I wouldn't give them a fair chance, but I am sure in the end they are just as good as any other necromancer ... Point is just have fun and play what you want ... You end up in the same place ...<br><br>Next if you are worried about faction, well then you should not be playing a Necromancer anyway ... Why would an evil character (yes Necromancy is &quot;evil&quot;) care about Faction with anyone except perhaps his own people. Besides faction is EASILY changed so don't even worry about starting faction.<br><br>Next, just know that Everquest is against you from the start. Necromancers are NOT wanted highly in groups at lower levels, but who cares? We are solo gods right? Well, that is right, but solo for 60 levels and you might be begging for a change once in a while. I solo'd mostly from 1-60 with a few groups then at 60-65 I grouped entirely in PoP ... once you hit 60+ people even ask for necros to join, everyone loves necros it seems since PoP release if you are 60+ I am not sure why the change has come about, but I love it ... I am 65 with every single spell from 1-65 except the 2 ancient ones which are worthless now anyway ... I do a ton of dmg and my 63 rogue pet and my 65 warrior pet do insane dmg ... I can honestly say I bring a lot to a group in almost any situation ... Group heal if needed, group mana transfer, single mana transfer, 70% undead slow, huge snare from 63 Embracing Darkness, huge dmg Dots from Funeral Pyre and Blood of Thule ... I can agro kite for my party with ease ... I can res at 93% if no cleric is around, I can summon corpses from the lost depths that might normally be hard as hell to recover ... Necromancers are the jack of all trades ... This is just my babbling lol , but if you have any questions about anything to do with a necromancer then email me at extasy_eclipse@yahoo.com ... <br><br>my character so far ... (without AA so he actually has more HP and mana etc, but it doesnt show that) <br><br><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/userinfo.html?char=348716" target="akztarg">http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/userinfo.html?char=348716</a></p><br /><span class="sm">----------------------------</span><br />As the Phoenix is reborn from the fires, so shall I be from the shadows. Fear the silence, for then I will strike. Fear the darkness for that is my home.</td></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform"><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%"><tr><td id="fs8"></td></tr></table>
